api_list.description:
Returns detailed sales tax data given the zip_code.
Request Body:
```
{
    "zip_code": "10010"
}
```

Output:
```
{
    "combined": { // total taxes
		"text": "8.875% (Combined)",
		"value": "0.08875"
	},
	"rate_Special": {
		"text": "0.375% (Special)",
		"value": "0.00375"
	},
	"rate_State": {
		"text": "4% (State)",
		"value": "0.04000"
	},
	"rate_City": {
		"text": "4.5% (City)",
		"value": "0.04500"
	}
}
```
